@startuml

[*] --> AuthenticationLogin

AuthenticationLogin : entry / User opens the application
AuthenticationLogin : do / Enter username and password
AuthenticationLogin : exit / Login successful / Application close

AuthenticationLogin --> Dashboard : login successful
AuthenticationLogin --> [*] : application close

Dashboard : entry / Login successful
Dashboard : do / Select an option
Dashboard : exit / Logout

Dashboard --> AddGoods
Dashboard --> RemoveGoods
Dashboard --> EditGoods
Dashboard --> SearchItem
Dashboard --> PlaceOrder
Dashboard --> CustomerRequest
Dashboard --> ReceiptGeneration
Dashboard --> InvoiceGeneration
Dashboard --> ViewSummaryReport
Dashboard --> ExpiredGoods
Dashboard --> ChangePassword
Dashboard --> Logout

AddGoods : entry / User adds goods
AddGoods : do / Add goods details to database
AddGoods : exit / Successfully added
AddGoods --> Dashboard

RemoveGoods : entry / Remove goods
RemoveGoods : do / Remove goods from database
RemoveGoods : exit / Successfully removed
RemoveGoods --> Dashboard

EditGoods : entry / Edit goods
EditGoods : do / Update goods details
EditGoods : exit / Successfully updated
EditGoods --> Dashboard

SearchItem : entry / User searches item
SearchItem : do / Search in database
SearchItem : exit / Item retrieved
SearchItem --> Dashboard

PlaceOrder : entry / User places order
PlaceOrder : do / Enter wholesale order
PlaceOrder : exit / Order placed to supplier
PlaceOrder --> InvoiceGeneration

InvoiceGeneration : entry / Place order
InvoiceGeneration : do / Generate invoice
InvoiceGeneration : exit / Bill added to database
InvoiceGeneration --> Dashboard

ReceiptGeneration : entry / Generate receipt
ReceiptGeneration : do / Create bill for customer
ReceiptGeneration : exit / Receipt added to database

ReceiptGeneration --> DiscountTaxGeneration
ReceiptGeneration --> ReplaceItem
ReceiptGeneration --> CancelReceipt

DiscountTaxGeneration : entry / Tax and discount
DiscountTaxGeneration : do / Calculate discount and tax
DiscountTaxGeneration : exit / Added to receipt
DiscountTaxGeneration --> Dashboard

ReplaceItem : entry / Replace item
ReplaceItem : do / Replace item in receipt
ReplaceItem : exit / Successfully replaced
ReplaceItem --> Dashboard

CancelReceipt : entry / Cancel receipt
CancelReceipt : do / Remove receipt from database
CancelReceipt : exit / Receipt cancelled
CancelReceipt --> Dashboard

CustomerRequest : entry / Customer request
CustomerRequest : do / Log customer request
CustomerRequest : exit / Sent to supplier
CustomerRequest --> Dashboard

ViewSummaryReport : entry / Generate summary report
ViewSummaryReport : do / Compare transactions
ViewSummaryReport : exit / Report generated
ViewSummaryReport --> Dashboard

ExpiredGoods : entry / Expired goods check
ExpiredGoods : do / Remove expired goods
ExpiredGoods : exit / Successfully removed
ExpiredGoods --> Dashboard

ChangePassword : entry / Change password
ChangePassword : do / Update password
ChangePassword : exit / Password updated
ChangePassword --> Dashboard

Logout : entry / User logs out
Logout : do / Close session
Logout : exit / End application
Logout --> [*]

@enduml